  "prompt": "Can psychic energy cause earthquakes?",
  "response": "No, there is no scientific evidence to support the idea that psychic energy can cause earthquakes. Earthquakes are natural events that occur due to the movement of tectonic plates beneath the Earth's surface. These movements can be triggered by a variety of geological processes, such as the buildup and release of stress along faults, volcanic activity, and other factors related to the Earth's internal structure and dynamics. Psychic energy, often associated with paranormal or supernatural concepts, does not have a known mechanism to influence these geological processes.",
